<paragraph id="A65BE18D47D6F1D068B8E2CFCEFE3810" pageId="21" pageNumber="60">Rock ledges (bedrock slabs); moisture regime: in soil pockets on rock. Forming cushions on almost flat rock slabs, in pockets of soil.</paragraph>
